      <description>To Prathun: Dude, your statement about the MPG trials maybe being too easy for the rewards boggles my mind. OOW was Sony's last real successful expansion. Look at the zones that are still heavily used even with DoN, DoDH, PoR and TSS. Don't laugh off the success you had with that expansion, rather go back and look at it, ask youself what did we hit there that made it so popular. Then incorporate that into your future expansions. Good challenges, great rewards and let's face it, the armor from Anguish overall is much better than anything since up to the TSS Raid Armor. You want to keep players and your job? Analyze the success, do your math on where the most zone activity is and what is being done there. TSS is a good expansion for the level upgrades, but you missed the boat entirely on your loot drops, whoever did your items needs to go back to past EQs and see what got people hot to grind and push to win. Innovation is a good thing but don't forget to keep your finger on the pulse of the people whose money pays your salary. EQ is a timesink, you're making it too much of a timesink for the return.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
